com.interpss.core.aclf.contingency.dep

Interface DepContingency

  • All Superinterfaces:
    BaseContingency, com.hazelcast.nio.serialization.DataSerializable, DepIEquivOutageBranch, DepIOutageIslanding, org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, NameTag, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    DepContingencyImpl

    public interface DepContingency
extends BaseContingency, DepIEquivOutageBranch, DepIOutageIslanding
    A representation of the model object 'Contingency'. A class for modeling a contingency

    The following features are supported:

    • Total Islands
    • Max Shifted Flow
    • Max Shift Flow Branch Id
    • Outage Branches
    • Island Buses
    • Equiv Outage Branches
    See Also:
    DepContingencyPackage.getDepContingency()
